WEBVTT

1
01:05:11.120 --> 01:05:12.030 
许多结了婚的夫妻……
A lot of married couples...

2
01:05:12.160 --> 01:05:13.832 
我和你爸要分手了
Your father and l are splitting up.

3
01:05:13.960 --> 01:05:15.393 
谢天谢地，太好不过了
Thank you. That's great.

4
01:05:15.520 --> 01:05:17.238 
我时间有点赶
It was just a matter of time.

5
01:05:17.360 --> 01:05:18.634 
我要去拿包裹
I'll go get the bags packed.

6
01:05:18.760 --> 01:05:20.159 
要走的时候通知一下
Let me know when we're ready to go.

7
01:05:20.280 --> 01:05:22.032 
布兰登，你就不能坐下呆一会儿？
Why don't you sit down, Brendan, for a second?

8
01:05:22.160 --> 01:05:23.673 
我们想说说我们怎么想的
We'll tell you what we're thinking.

9
01:05:23.800 --> 01:05:26.189 
要是你同意的话
You see if you agree.

10
01:05:26.320 --> 01:05:29.198 
达成共识？
A consensus?.

11
01:05:29.360 --> 01:05:31.316 
天方夜谭，好吧
That's novel. Okay.

12
01:05:32.760 --> 01:05:36.753 
罗伯特：你妈爱上了托尼
ROBERT: Your mother has fallen in love with Tony.

13
01:05:36.880 --> 01:05:39.348 
他们决定搬到托尼的公寓里同居，然后……
They're gonna be moving into his apartment for awhile and...

14
01:05:39.480 --> 01:05:40.435 
就这样
Yeah.

15
01:05:40.560 --> 01:05:42.312 
有人给这房子报了价
We've had an offer on this house.

16
01:05:42.440 --> 01:05:45.113 
虽然只有房价的一半，不过我们准备卖了
It's half what it's worth, but we're gonna take it.

